3. TCL & DCL COMMANDS

a) TCL COMMANDS 
 1. Commit 
 2. Rollback 
 3. Savepoint


mysql> set autocommit=0;
Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.00 sec)

mysql> insert into tchr(Id,name,salary)values(1,'Renu',24000);
Query OK, 1 row affected (0.00 sec)

mysql> select * from tchr;
